Sailor

Wrapped like a star,
  seas wave-styled,
      the bright wreaths

  glow in the air,
in wavy shells,
       in the shine of the sun.
       In the weight,
       the burning longest,

and the sea of the golden dusk
  so soft and deep,
  as the air clad.

H.D.

- HD
